        },
        "body": "Problem Added\r\nLeetCode Problem 67: Add Binary\r\n\r\nThis pull request adds implementations of the “Add Binary” problem in both C++ and Java.\r\nThe solutions take two binary strings as input and return their sum as a binary string using an efficient O(n) approach.\r\n\r\nSolution Highlights:\r\n1) Implemented using string manipulation and carry handling (no built-in binary conversion).\r\n2) Works correctly for variable-length binary inputs.\r\n3) Includes console-based input/output for user testing.\r\n4) Code is structured, readable, and consistent across both languages.",
